パッケージ com.shimizukenta.jsonhub

インタフェース JsonHubBuilder

既知の実装クラスのリスト:
AbstractJsonHubBuilder
public interface JsonHubBuilder
This interface is implements of building JsonHub instance.

This class is used in JsonReader, JsonHubFromPojoParser.

To build NullJsonHub instance, nullValue(), build(Object).
To build TrueJsonHub instance, trueValue(), build(Object).
To build FalseJsonHub instance, falseValue(), build(Object).
To build StringJsonHub instance, string(CharSequence), string(JsonString), build(Object).
To build NumberJsonHub instance, number(int), number(long), number(float), number(double), number(Number), number(CharSequence), build(int), build(long), build(float), build(double), build(Object).
To build ArrayJsonHub instance, array(), array(JsonHub...), array(List), emptyArray().
To build ObjectJsonHub instance, object(), object(Collection), object(JsonObjectPair...), object(Map), emptyObject().

To build JsonObjectPair instance, pair(CharSequence, boolean), pair(CharSequence, int), pair(CharSequence, long), pair(CharSequence, float), pair(CharSequence, double), pair(CharSequence, Object), pair(JsonString, boolean), pair(JsonString, int), pair(JsonString, long), pair(JsonString, float), pair(JsonString, double), pair(JsonString, Object).

    • build

      AbstractJsonHub build​(java.lang.Object v)
      Returns AbstractJsonHub instance (NULL, TRUE, FALSE, STRING or NUMBER).

      If v == null, return NullJsonHub instance.
      If v instanceof Boolean, return TrueJsonHub or FalseJsonHub instance.
      If v instanceof CharSequence, return StringJsonHub instance.
      If v instanceof JsonString, return StringJsonHub instance.
      If v instanceof Number, return NumberJsonHub instance.

      パラメータ:
      v - Object value
      戻り値:
      AbstractJsonHub (NULL, TRUE, FALSE, STRING or NUMBER)
      例外:
      JsonHubBuildException - if type is unsupported
